sold exclusive rights to the nuptials to People magazine.
   Brown is a University of Maryland graduate and former ``Miss
Georgetown'' who appeared in Playboy magazine's 1988 ``Women of
Washington'' feature.
   She met the host of ``The Pat Sajak Show'' and ``Wheel of
Fortune'' at the celebrity opening of a restaurant in Irvine,
Calif., in 1988.
   Few celebrities were counted among the 100-150 guests, but
Sajak's wheel turner and close friend, Vanna White, was spotted
dodging from the church.
</TEXT>
